							<span class="text-2xl">ðŸŽ¬</span>
							<div>
								<strong class="text-slate-900 block mb-1 font-bold">Cinematic Storytelling</strong>
								<span class="text-sm leading-relaxed italic">A fan of movies that challenge our understanding of the future, technology, and the human condition.</span>
							</div>
						</li>
						<li class="flex gap-4 items-start">
							<span class="text-2xl">ðŸ¤–</span>
							<div>
								<strong class="text-slate-900 block mb-1 font-bold">AI Philosophy</strong>
								<span class="text-sm leading-relaxed italic">Hobbyist explorer of the philosophical and creative implications of artificial intelligence.</span>
							</div>
						</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</section>

			<!-- CTA -->
			<section class="mt-24 p-10 bg-slate-900 rounded-3xl text-center space-y-6 text-white shadow-2xl">
				<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold">Interested in collaborating?</h2>
				<p class="text-slate-400 max-w-md mx-auto">
					I'm always open to discussing backend architecture, AI integration, or electronic music.
